quran[206]{c,v,t}:
  7,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim, Saad.firo …óee alkule wulinoomo efu…ó…óoode simoore bakharah(nagge nge)."
  7,2,"∆äum de ko deftere Jippinaande e maa…óa, wata …ďitteende won e …ďernde maa e mayre ; fii yo a waajor nde, ko nde waaju wonan de gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďeen."
  7,3,"Njokkee ko Jippinaa e mon kon immorde ka Joomi mon, wota on njokku gah …óuum, weldii…ďe, fam…óii ko mbaactorto…óon."
  7,4,"∆äuu…óii e ce'e …óe min kalki! Lepte Amen …óen ari e majje jemma hi…ďe waalii …óaanii, maa hara ko …ďe fo'ofii…ďe √Īalawma."
  7,5,"Noddaandu ma…ď…ďe ndun …ďaawo lepte Amen …óen arde …ďe, wonaano si naa bi'igol : ""Minen min laatino too√Īoo…ďe""."
  7,6,"Wollahi ma min La…ďditoyo …ďeen …ďe (Min) Nulnoo e muen, Ma Min La…ďnditoyo kadi Nulaa…ďe …ďe."
  7,7,"Ma min pillanoroyo …ďe (golle ma…ď…ďe …óen) e ganndal. min ngonaano wirnii…ďe.…ďe (tawtoraaka)"
  7,8,"Manndakke=(pe'esir…ói )(…ďetir…ói) √Ďande, ko …ói goonga. Kala mo manndake (mo∆ī∆īi …óen) teddi, ko …ďeen …óoon ngoni maloytee…ďe …ďen."
  7,9,"Kala mo manndakke (mo∆ī∆īi) mun foygitii=hoyi, ko …ďeen …óoon ngoni sooyinir…ďe pittaali mu'uen sa…ďu ko …ďe laatinoo he…ďee njedda Aayeeje amen …óeen."
  7,10,"Mi woo…óniiii minn Newinanii on ke leydi, min mba…óani on e mayri nguuree. (Kono) fam…óii ko njettoton."
  7,11,"Mi woo…óndii min tagii on, refti min mbaadini on, refti min mbi'ani maleykaaji …óiin : ""cujjanee Aadama"", …ďe cujji, si wonaa Ibliisa, o jeyanooka e sujju…ďe …ďen."
  7,12,"O Daali : ""Ko ha…ó maa nde cujjataa nde mi yamir-maa?"" owi'i : ""mi…óo …ďuri mo mo∆ī∆īude : A tagii kam immorde e Yiite, A tagii mo immorde e loopal""."
  7,13,"O Daali : ""Jippo toon, haananaama nde mawnintinto…óaa toon. yaltu, an ko a jeyaa…óo e hoy…ďe …ďeen""."
  7,14,"[Ibliisa] wi'i : ""Nee…ďnitanam haa √Īande …ďe immintintee""."
  7,15,"[Alla] Daali : ""aan, ko a jeyaa…óo e nee…ďinantee…ďe …ďeen""."
  7,16,"[Ibliisa] wi'i : ""Sabu ko mbewnir…óaa kam koo, ma mi joo…óano …ďe ka laawol maa po'ociingol.ngol"
  7,17,"Refti mi ardiranat…ďe …ďe yeeso ma…ď…ďe e …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe, e ka e √Īaame ma…ď…ďe e ka nane ma…ď…ďe. a tawataa ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e ma…ď…ďe ko yettoo…ďe [Ma]""."
  7,18,"[Alla] Daali : ""Yaltu toon, ko a √ĪiŇčaa…óo diiwaa…óo. Kala jokku…óo ma e ma…ď…ďe, ma Mi kebbiiroye Jahannama onon denndaangal""."
  7,19,"""Eeyma yo Aadama, ho…ó an e …ďeyngu maa ka Aljanna, √Īaamee kala nokku ka njii…ó-…óon ; wota tan on …ďa…óto kii …óoo lekki, sakko laato…óon e too√Īoo…ďe …ďen""."
  7,20,"Seytaane sowinsini …ďe, fii yo o fe√Ī√Īinan …ďe ko suu…óaa e ma…ď…ďe e awraaji ma…ď…ďe, o wi'i : ""Joomi mon ha…óiraani on ki lekkil si wanaa fii wata on laato maleykaaji maa laato…óon duumotoo…ďe [ka Aljanna]""."
  7,21,"O woo…óndani …ďe o wi'i : ""miin komi e…ďee laa…ďanoo…ďe on"".deedi"
  7,22,"O hodiri …ďe koomte. Nde …ďe mee…ónoo elekki he, awraaji ma…ď…ďe …óiin pee√Īani …ďe, …ďe mba…óti he…ďe curritora kaaki Aljanna …óiin. Joomi ma…ď…ďe noddi …ďe : ""E Mi ha…óaano on e ki lekki, Mi wi'ani on : Pellet, seytaane ko ga√Īo mon …ďanngu…óo?!(""pee√Ī…óo.)"
  7,23,"∆Āe mbi'i : ""Joomi amen, min too√Īii ko'e amen. Si A yaafaakii amen njurmi…óaa amen, ma min njeye e sooy…ďe …ďeen""."
  7,24,"[Alla] Daali : ""njippee (ka leydi), yoga mon ko a√Ī…ďe yoga. Hino woodani on ka leydi ton √Īii…ďirde e dakamme haa saanga""."
  7,25,"[Alla] Daali : ""Ko (ka leydi) ton nguuroton, ko ton kadi maayoton, ko e mayri kadi njaltinoyte…óon""."
  7,26,"Eehey mon yo …ďi…ó…ďe Aadam! GooŇč…óii min njippinii e mo'on comci cuhrat…ói awraaji mon …óin e cu…óaari. -Ko comci kulol …óin noon …ďuri mu∆ī∆īude.- Ko …óuum jeyaa…óum e Aayeeje Alla. mbeleejo'o, kam…ďe …ďe mbaajitoto."
  7,27,"Ko onon yo …ďi…ó…ďe Aadama! Wata seytaane fitinir on wano o yaltinirnoo baabiraa…ďe mon …ďen ka Aljanna, homo …ďoora e ma…ď…ďe comci ma…ď…ďe …óin fii yo hollu …ďe awraaji ma…ď…ďe …óin. Pellet, homo reeni on kaŇčko e gorol makko ngol nokku ka on yi'ataa …ďe. minen min mba…óii seytaaneeji …óin beldii…ói …ďeen …ďen goo…óintaa."
  7,28,"Si …ďe mba…óii paŇčkare, …ďe mb'a : ""min tawru …óum baabiraa…ďe amen …ďeen, ko Alla yamiri min …óum"". Maaku : ""Pellet, Alla yamirtaa paŇčkare. E on wowlay e hoore Alla ko on nganndaa?!""."
  7,29,"Maaku : ""Joomi am yamirii nuun…óal. √Ďii…ďnon jeece mon …óeen nokku kala e ka juuloton, tororon mo la…ď…ďinangol mo diine kan. Ko wano o Fu…ó…óori on non ndu…ótorton""."
  7,30,"Fedde goo o fewnii, fedde goo majjere nden jojji e hoore ma…ď…ďe. Kam…ďe …ďe njogitike seytaaneeji …óin weldii…ďe gaanin Alla, kam…ďe hi…ďe cikka ko …ďe feew…ďe."
  7,31,"Eey mon …ďi…ó…ďe Aadama, ∆īettee cu…óaari mon ndin nokku kala ka njuuloton. √Ďaamee njaron wota on …ďurtin. Pellet, KaŇčko o yi…óaa …ďurtinoo…ďe …ďeen."
  7,32,"Maaku : ""Ko hommbo harmini cu…óaari Alla ndi O Yaltinani jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďeen, e laa…ďu…ói …óin ka arsikeeji?"" Maaku : ""∆äin …ďen gooŇč…óiin…ďe ka nguurndam aduna woodani, heeranii…ói […ďe] √Ďande Darngal"". Ko wano non min pirtirta Aayeeje …óen, wonan de yim…ďe anndoo…ďe."
  7,33,"Maaku : ""Joomi am ko Harmini : ko paaŇčkare …óen -ko fee√Īi e majje ko suu…óii-, e bakkaat, e bewrugol ko aldaa e goonga, e nde cirkanton Mo kon ko O Jippinanaani …óuum hujja, e nde wowloton e Alla ko on nganndaa."
  7,34,"Hino woodani kala mofte( le√Īol)lajal. Si lajal ma…ď…ďe ngal arii, …ďe nee…ďtitantaake saa'i gooto, …ďe ngardinantaake kadi."
  7,35,"Ehey mon …ďi…ó…ďe Aadama! Si aroyii e mon Nulaa…ďe jeyaa…ďe e mo'on, …ďe no fillanoo on Aayeeje Am, kala kul…óo [Alla] o mo∆ī∆īini [golle], kulol alanaa …ďen …óon, wanaa kam…ďe kadi …ďe cunoytaako."
  7,36,"∆Āeen yeddu…ďe Aayeeje amen …óeen …ďe townitanii e he…óe, ko …ďen ngooni yim…ďe Yiite, kam…ďe ko …ďe luttoo…ďe toon."
  7,37,"Alaa …ďur…óo too√Īu…óo haa hewta on pekindii…óo e Alla fenaande, maa o yeddi Aayeeje Makko …óen? …ďeen ke…ďat …ďe ge…óal ma…ď…ďe ngal e binndoodi ndin ; haa si Nulaa…ďe amen [waroo…ďe] …ďen ngarii …ďe, …ďe mbara …ďe, …ďe mbia : ""Ko hoito kon ko ndewayno…óon gaanin Alla [woni]?!"" …ďe mbia : ""∆äi majjirii amen"". ∆Āe ceeditoo e ko'e ma…ď…ďe, won de …ďe laatino yeddu…ďe."
  7,38,"[Maleykaaji] mbi'a : ""Naate e moftaaji, gooŇč…óii yawtii adii mon immorde e jinna e yim…ďe ka ndeer Yiite"". Tuma kala nde le√Īol naati, ngol hu…óa banndu ngol . Haa si …ďe tawtindirii toon …ďe denndaanal, sakkitii…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďeen wi'ana aram…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďeen : ""Joomi amen! Ko …ďee majjini min : Okku …ďe lepte cowan…óe e Yiite ngen"". O Daala : ""Hino woodani kala [mon] cowan…óe, kono on ganndaa""."
  7,39,"Aram…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen mbi'ana sakkitii…ďe …ďeen : ""Alanaa on e dow amen …ďural, mee…óiree lepte …óen sabu kon ko paggitotono…óon""."
  7,40,"Pellet, …ďeen yeddu…ďe Aayeeje amen …óeen, …ďe townitanii …óe, …ďe udditantaake dame kammuuli …óin, …ďe naatataa kadi Aljanna haa ngelooba naata e wuddere meselal. Ko wano non Men njo…ďirto …ďon…ďe …ďeen."
  7,41,"Hino woodani …ďe ka Jahannama nda…ó…óudi, no dow ma…ď…ďe kadi kippoodi. Ko wanon non min njo…ďirta too√Īoo…ďe …ďeen."
  7,42,"∆Āeen goo…óin…ďe …ďe ngolli mo∆ī∆īu…ói - min pawataa woŇčkii si wanaa ko ki waawi - Ko …ďen …óon woni yim…ďe Aljanna : kam…ďe ko …ďe duumotoo…ďe ton."
  7,43,"Men …ďoori e …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen konnaagu, caatli …óiin no ila senngo ley ma…ď…ďe, …ďe mbi'a : ""jettoorje ngoodani Alla on peewnu…óo amen e …óuum …óoo, men ngonaano feewoo…ďe si Alla fewnaano amen. GooŇč…óii Nulaa…ďe Joomi amen …ďeen ngaddii goonga"". ∆Āe noddee si ko woni : ""Oon …óon moo…óon Aljanna, on ndonnaama mo, sabu kon ko ngollatno…óon""."
  7,44,"Yim…ďe Aljanna …ďeen noddi yim…ďe Yiite …ďen, si ko woni : ""GooŇč…óii min tawii ko Joomi amen fodi min kon ko goonga. Onon kadi on tawii ko Joom mon fodi on kon ko goonga?"" ∆Āe mbi'i : ""Eyyo"". Noddoowo nodda hakkunde ma…ď…ďe won de : Kuddi Alla ndin wonii e too√Īoo…ďe …ďeen,"
  7,45,"∆Āeen sakkotoo…ďe=falatoobe gah e laawol Alla ngol, …ďe …óa…ď…ďana ngol oo√Īorde, kam…ďe kadi ko …ďe yeddu…ďe laakara""."
  7,46,"Heedo no hakkunde ma…ď…ďe. Hino e dow tulde La'raafi nden wor…ďe he…ďe nganndira kala e maande mum ∆Āe nodda yim…ďe Aljanna …ďeen, si ko woni : ""Kisial woni e mon!"". ∆Āe naataani mo kono he…ďe tam∆īinii."
  7,47,"Si jii…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen pewtiniraa …ďannge yim…ďe Yiite …ďeen, …ďe mbi'a : ""Joomi amen! Wata A wa…ótdu amen e yim…ďe too√Īoo…ďe …ďeen""."
  7,48,"Yim…ďe La'raafi …ďen noddi wor…ďe, hi…ďe nganndira …ďeen maandeeji ma…ď…ďe, …ďe mbia : ""Nafaali on moo…ďugol mon [jawle], e kon ko laatino…óon hi…óon mawnintinoo!""."
  7,49,"E ko …ďee …óoo woondirno…óon [won de] Alla memintaa …ďe yurmeende?! Naatee Aljanna! Kulol alanaa on, wanaa onon ngoni ko sunoytoo…ďe."
  7,50,"Yim…ďe Yiite …ďeen noddi yim…ďe Aljanna …ďe, si ko woni : ""njuppee e amen ndiyam, maa kon ko Alla arsiki on"". ∆Āe mbi'a: ""Pellet, Alla harmini …óin …ói…ói e heefer…ďe …ďen"
  7,51,"∆Āeen jogitorii…ďe diine mum kan belaa…óe e fijindaaru, nguurndam aduna hodi …ďe. hannde min njejjitiray …ďe no …ďe njejjitirnoo hawrugol √Ďalaande ma…ď…ďe ndee, e kon ko …ďe njeddiranoo Aayeeje amen …óen."
  7,52,"GooŇč…óii min ngaddanii …ďe deftere, min fpirti nde e dow gaanndal, ko nde peewal e yurmeende …ďen yim…ďe gooŇč…óinoo…ďe."
  7,53,"Hara he…ďe kabbii si wanaa battane mum …óen? √Ďalnde battane (firo) mayre arata, yejjitunoo…ďe …óum …ďeen ko adii wi'ay : ""GooŇč…óii Nulaa…ďe Joomi amen …ďeen ngaddii goonga. Hara tefoo…ďe no woodani min …ďe tefana min? Maa min nduttee [aduna] min ngolla ko wanaa ko min ngollaatnoo?"" GooŇč…óii …ďe hayrinii wonkiiji ma…ď…ďe ; kon ko …ďe fekinotonoo majjiri…ďe."
  7,54,"Pellet, Joomi mon ko Alla, On Taku…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin e nder bal…óe jeegoo, refti O fotondiri ka hoore Arsi. Himo suddira jemma on √Īalawma, hi…ói …óa…ď…ďindira no yaccorii. Naange ngen e lewru ndun e koode …óen ko eltiraa…ói yamiroore Makko. Paamee ko KaŇčko heeranii tagoore nde e yamiroore nden. Mawnii mawngu Alla, Jey…óo Winndere ndeen."
  7,55,"Noddiiree Joomi mon yaŇčkinaare e gunndoo. Pellet, KaŇčko O Yi…óaa jaggitoo…ďe (…ďenyawtoo…ďe. Keeri)."
  7,56,"Wata on mbonnu ke leydi …ďaawo mo∆ī∆īugol ndi. Noddiree mo kulol e …óamam'u. Pellet, yurmeende Alla nden no …ďadii mo∆ī∆īim…ďe …ďen."
  7,57,"Ko KaŇčko woni Nuloowo keneeli …óin welo-welo yeeso Yurmeende Makko nden. Haa si ndu ronndike duule teddunde, Men cogga nde e leydi maayndi [yoori], min njippina e mayri ndiyam, min njaltinira …óam kala dim…óe. Ko non min njaltiniroyta maay…ďe …ďen. mbeleeo'o, on mbaactoto."
  7,58,"Leydi mo∆ī∆īiri ndin, pu…ói mayri no yaltira duŇčayee Joomi mayri ; ndin ndi (pu…ói mum) boni, ndi yaltintaa si wanaa no sa…ótiri. Ko non min …ďannginirta Aayeeje …óeen woan de yim…ďe yettoo…ďe [Joomi muen]."
  7,59,"Wollahiii min nulii Nuuhu e yim…ďe makko …ďen, o maaki : ""Ko onon yo yim…ďe am, ndewee Alla. dewetee…óo alanaa on ko woori mo. min mi…óo hulani on lepte √Ďalaande mawnde""."
  7,60,"Hooree…ďe mbatu yim…ďe makko …ďen wi'i : ""Minen m…óen ma njia e nder majjere …ďanngunde""(.fee√Īnde)"
  7,61,"O maaki : ""Eey mon yim…ďe am, majjere (woo) alaa e am ; ko woni min, ko Nulaa…óo immorde ka Jey…óo Winndere nden."
  7,62,"Mi…óo yottina e mon Nule Joomi am, mi…óo laa…ďana on (reedu), mi…óo anndi ka Alla ko on nganndaa."
  7,63,"E on kaawa fii waajo no ari on immorde ka Joomi mon e dow gorko jeyaa…óo e mo'on?! Fii yo o jertin on e fii yo on ndeento, mbelejo'o, on (ke…ďat) yurmeende [Alla]."
  7,64,"∆Āe njeddi mo. minn nda…óndii mo e …ďeen won du…ďe e makko ka laana, min njooli …ďeen yeddu…ďe Aayeeje amen …óeen. Pellet, …ďe laatino yim…ďe wum…óu…ďe."
  7,65,"[min Nulii] kadi fa'ade e Aadinkoo…ďe …ďeen, musi…ó…óo ma…ď…ďe on Huudi. O maaki : ""Ko onon yo yim…ďe am, ndewee Alla, dewetee…óo alanaa on ko woori mo. E on kulataa [Mo]?!""."
  7,66,"Hooree…ďe mbatu …ďen yeddu…ďe e yim…ďe makko …ďen mbi'i : ""minen mi…óen ma njia'e e …óayre, minen mi…óen cikku maa jeyaa…óo e fenoo…ďe …ďeen""."
  7,67,"O maaki : ""Eey mon yim…ďe am, …óayre (woo) alaa e am ; ko woni min, ko Nulaa…óo immorde ka Jey…óo Winndere ndeen."
  7,68,"Mi…óo yottina e mo'on Nule Joomi am, min (non) ko mi laa…ďanoo on (reedu), koolnii…óo."
  7,69,"E kaawo fii waajo no ari on immorde ka Joomi mon e dow gorko jeyaa…óo e mo'on, fii yo o jeertin on?! ciftoree tuma nde O wa…ónoo on lomtii…ďe …ďaawo yim…ďe Nuuhu …ďen, O …ďeydi on ka tagoore semmbe. ciftoree dokke Alla …óe mbelejo'o, on malete."
  7,70,"∆Āe mbi'i : ""E a ar e amen fii yo min ndew Alla tan, min ngacca kon ko baabiraa…ďe amen …ďeen ndewatnoo?! Awa addan amen ko podan…óaa men kon (e lepte) si tawii ko a jeyaa…óo e gooŇčnu…ďe …ďeen."
  7,71,"O maaki : ""GooŇč…óii yanii e mon immorde ka Joomi mon so…ďe (lepte) e tikkere. E on mbee√Īdat e am fii in…óe …óe innu…óon onon e baabiraa…ďe mo'on, Alla Jippinaali fii majje hujja?! padee! min, won dude e mo'on, ko mi jeyaa…óo e fat…ďe …ďen""."
  7,72,"Min nda…óniri mo e …ďeen won du…ďe e makko yurmeende amen, men ta∆īi …ďabbe …ďeen yeddu…ďe Aayeeje amen …óeen, …ďe laatanooki gooŇč…óin…ďe."
  7,73,"[Men Nulii] kadi faade e Samuuda'en, musi…ó…óo ma…ď…ďe on Saalihu, o maaki : ""Eehey mon yim…ďe am, ndewee Alla. dewetee…óo alanaa on ko woori mo. GooŇč…óii arii on …ďanngannduyee immorde ka Joomi mon : mbaa ko ngeelooba Alla ma'ande wonan de on, tertee mba √Īaama ka leydi Alla, wata on memir ba bone sakko lepte muusu…óe nannga on""."
  7,74,"Ciftoree tuma nde o wa…ónoo on lomtii…ďe Aadinkoo…ďe …ďeen, o weernii on ka leydi ho…óon njogitoo e ndantaaji mayri ku…ďeeje, ho…óon lesa pelle (wa…óon) cuu…ói. Ciftoree dokke Alla …óeen, wota on …ďurtinir ka leydi ko on bonnoo…ďe."
  7,75,"Hooree…ďe mbatu mawninkinii…ďe …ďeen e yim…ďe makko …ďeen mbi'ani gooŇč…óin…ďe lo'inaa…ďe …ďen e ma…ď…ďe : ""E ho…óon nganndi won de Saalihu ko Nulaa…óo immorde ka Joomi makko?"" ∆Āe mbi'i : minen ko men gooŇč…óin…ďe ko o Nulidaa e mum koon""."
  7,76,"∆Āen mawnintinii…ďe wi'i : ""Minen, kon ko ngooŇč…óin…óon, ko men yeddu…ďe …óum""."
  7,77,"∆Āe mborii ngeelooba ban, …ďe mawninkini gah e yamiroore Joomi ma…ď…ďe ndeen, …ďe mbi'i : ""Ko an yo Saalihu, addan amen kon ko podanna…óaa amen (e lepte) si tawii ko a jeyaa…óo e Nulaa…ďe …ďeen""."
  7,78,"Dillaango ngon nanngi …ďe, …ďe mba…ótini ka ko…óooli ma…ď…ďe ko …ďe jiccii…ďe-…óaanii(.jus…ďe)"
  7,79,"O ruŇčtii …ďe o maaki : ""eey mon yo yim…ďe am, gooŇč…óii mi yottinii e mon Nulal Joomi am ngal mi laa…ďanii on (reedu), konon, on nji…óaa laa…ďoo…ďe (reedu) …ďeen."
  7,80,"E luuti, tuma nde o maakannoo yim…ďe makko …ďen : "" E o ngaray e paŇčkare …óe go…ó…óo goo adaaki on e mun e Winndere ndeen?!"
  7,81,"Onon ho…óon njottoo e wor…ďe …ďeen tuuyo ngaccon rew…ďe …ďeen! Si ko woni, onon ko on yim…ďe fantim…ďe(.…ďurtin…ďe)."
  7,82,"Jaabawol yim…ďe makko e …ďee wonaano si wanaa ko …ďe mbi'i : ""njaaltinee …ďe ka ho…óordemon ; kam…ďe ko …ďe yim…ďe la…ď…ďintintoo…ďe""."
  7,83,"Min da…óndi mo kaŇčko e yim…ďe makko …ďeen, si wonaa debbo makko on ; on…óon heddodino e (leptaa…ďe) …ďeen."
  7,84,"Min saa∆īini to…ďo e ma…ď…ďe. Ndaarii ko holno battane bon…ďe …ďe…ón laatornoo?"
  7,85,"[Men Nulii] kadi faade e Madyana, musi…ó…óo ma…ď…ďe on Su'aybu, o maaki : ""eehey mon yim…ďe am, ndewee Alla. dewetee…óo alanaa on ko woori mo. GooŇč…óii …ďanngannduyee arii on immorde ka Joomi mon. Timminee …ďetir…óe …óiin e manndikke …óeen, wata on ustan yim…ďe …ďeen piiji ma…ď…ďe …óiin, wota on mbonnu ko leydi …ďaawo mo∆ī∆īugol ndi. Ko …óuum moo…óon …ďuri on mo∆ī∆īannde si on laatike gooŇč…óiin…ďe""."
  7,86,"Wata on njoo…óo e kala laawol, ho…óon kammba, ho…óon sakko=paddooo e laawol Alla ngol …ďeen gooŇč…óin…ďe Mo, ho…óon …óa…ď…ďana ngol oo√Īaare. ngannditee tuma nde ngonndo…óon see…óaa…ďe o …óu…ó…óini on. Ndaaree holno battane bonnoo…ďe …ďe laatornoo."
  7,87,"Si wonii fedde e moo…óon gooŇč…óinii kon ko Nuliraa e mun, fedde goo gooŇč…óinaani, mu√Ī√Īee haa Alla √Īaawa hakkunde me'n. Ko KaŇčko …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e √Īaawoo…ďe …ďeen."
  7,88,"Mbatu mawnintiniingu e yim…ďe makko …ďen mbi'i : ""Ko maa men yaltine an Su'aybu, e …ďeen gooŇč…óin…ďe won dude e maa…óa ka saare amen, maa ndutto…óon e diina amen"". -o maaki : ""Hay si tawii ko men a√Īu…ďe […óuum]?""."
  7,89,"Goo…óii (haray) min pekifindike e hoore Alla fenaande si men nduttike e diina mon …ďaawo nde Alla da…óndi men e makka. Alanaa min ndee men rnduttoo e makka si wanaa nde Alla Joomi amen muuyi. Joomi amen yaajanii kala huunde ganndal. Ko e Alla en pawii. Joomi amen, √Īaawir hakkunde amen e yim…ďe amen …ďen goonga, ko An woni …ďur…óo mo∆ī∆īude e √Īaawoo…ďe …ďeen""."
  7,90,"Mbatu …ďen yeddu…ďe e yim…ďe makko …ďeen mb'i : ""Pellet, si on njokkii Su'aybu, onon ontuma ko on hayru…ďe"".(pertu…ďe)"
  7,91,"Dillaango ngoon nanngi …ďe, …ďe wa…ótini ka ko…óooli ma…ď…ďe ko …ďe jiccii…ďe-…óaanii."
  7,92,"∆Āeen yeddnnunoo…ďe Su'aybu, (…ďe kalkorino) wa si …ďe mee…óaa wuurude e ngon [ho…óo]. ∆Āeen yeddunoo…ďe Su'aybu, …ďe laatino kam…ďe woni hayru…ďe …ďen."
  7,93,"O …óuurni …ďe, o maaki : ""eey mon yim…ďe am, gooŇč…óii mi njottinii e mo'on Nule Joomi am …óeen mi laa…ďanii on (reedu). E ko hoolno mi surnortoo e yim…ďe yeddu…ďe?!""."
  7,94,"Men nulaali e saare hay e Annbaajo, si wanaa minn nanngirii yim…ďe mayre …ďeen sa…óteende e lorra mbelejo'o, …ďe yankinoto."
  7,95,"Refti min mba…ótitiri nokku bone on mo∆ī∆īere, haa …ďe …óuu…ói, …ďe mbi'i : ""GooŇč…óii sa…ótteende e neweende he…ďiino baabiraa…ďe amen …ďeen"". min nanngiri …ďe e juhal, tawi kam…ďe …ďe so'aa anndude.(tinaana)."
  7,96,"Sinno yim…ďe ce'e …ďeen ngooŇč…óinno …ďe kuli (Joomi ma…ď…ďe), min udditanayno …ďe mo∆ī∆īereeji immorde ka Kammu e ka leydi. Kono …ďe njedd, min nanngitiri …ďe (lepte …óeen) kon ko …ďe paggittoonoo."
  7,97,"Hara yim…ďe ce'e …ďene kooli nde lepte amen …óen ngarataa …ďe jemma, hara he…ďe …óaanii?"
  7,98,"Kaa hara yim…ďe ce'e …ďeen kooli nde lepte amen …óen ngarataa …ďe ka mbeeto, hara hi…ďe pija?"
  7,99,"E …ďe kooli pewje Alla …óeen? Hoolotaako pewje Alla …óeen si wanaa yim…ďe hayru…ďe …ďeen."
  7,100,"E …ďannganaali …ďeen ronoo…ďe leydi …ďeen …ďaawo (halkagol) yim…ďe mayri …ďeen, won de si min muuyuno min meminirayno …ďe [lepte …óen] bakkatuji ma…ď…ďe …óin? min tappa e …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óeen hara kam…ďe …ďe nanataa."
  7,101,"∆äeen ce'e, mi…óen fillano maa kumpite majje. GooŇč…óii nulaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen ngaddanii …ďe …ďanngannduyeeji, …ďe ngonaano gooŇč…óinoo…ďe ko …ďe njeddi kon ko adii. Ko wano nii All notirta e …ďer…óe heefer…ďe …ďeen."
  7,102,"min tawaano ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e ma…ď…ďe huu…ďoo…ďe ahadi ; si ko men tawi, ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e ma…ď…ďe ko yaltu…ďe. …óoftaare"
  7,103,"Refti minn Nulidi …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe Muusaa e Maandeeji amen …óin haa e Fir'awna e mbatu mu'um, …ďe yeddi …ói. Ndaaru ko honno battane bonnoo…ďe …ďeen laatornoo."
  7,104,"Muusaa maaki : ""eeheyma Fir'awna, miin komi nulaa…óo immorde ka Jey…óo winndere ndeen"
  7,105,"No haand i e am nde mi wowlataa e Alla si wanaa goonga. GooŇč…óii mi addanii on …ďanngannduyee immorde ka Joomi mon. neldu e …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila …ďen."
  7,106,"[Fir'awna] wi'i : ""Si tawii a ardii e maande, addu nde si tawii ko a jeyaa…óo e gooŇč…óuu…ďe …ďeen""."
  7,107,"O wernii weduru makko ndun, jaka ko ndu mboo…ódi=ngoolwa …ďanngundi."
  7,108,"O yaltini junngo makko ngon, jaka yoo ko ngo ranwungo wonannde ndaaroo…ďe …ďen."
  7,109,"Mbatu yim…ďe Fir'awna …ďen mbi'i : ""Pellet, oo, ko mbileejo ganndu…óo""."
  7,110,"""O faala yaltinnde on ka leydi mo'on"". -""Ko hol…óum njamirton?"""
  7,111,"∆Āe mbi'i : ""Nee…ďnu mo e musi…ó…óo makko on, nulaa e ce'e …óeen moo…ďoo…ďe (mbile)"".wilee…ďe"
  7,112,"∆Āe ngadane kala mbileejo ganndu…óo."
  7,113,"wilee…ďe …ďeen ari Fir'awna …ďe mbi'i : ""Hara njo…ďdi no woodani min, si min ngonii fool…ďe …ďeen?"""
  7,114,"O wi'i : ""Eyyo, haray on jeyaama e …ďa…ótinaa…ďe …ďeen""."
  7,115,"∆Āe mbi'i : ""eehe yma Muusaa, si …óa yi…ói ko nde bugoto…óaa, maa men wona (adotoo…ďe) bugagol"".(beddagol)"
  7,116,"O maaki : ""Bugee(mbedde)"". Nde …ďe bugii, (mbeddi )…ďe mbil…óii gite yim…ďe …ďeen, …ďe kul…ďini …ďe, …ďe ngddi mbilewu mawnungu."
  7,117,"minn mbahyini e Muusaa won de : ""Bugo tuggordu maa ndun weduru"". Jaka yoo hindi mo…óa ko …ďe pepekindotonoo."
  7,118,"Goonga on fee√Īi, ko …ďe ngollaynoo kon [fof] boni."
  7,119,"∆Āe poolaa …óoon …ďe kooti ko …ďe ja'asu…ďe."
  7,120,"Wilee…ďe …ďeen nduuyi cujji."
  7,121,"∆Āe mbi'i : ""min ngooŇč…óinii Jey…óo winndere ndeen,"
  7,122,"Joomum Muusaa e Haaruuna""."
  7,123,"Fir'awna wi'i : ""On ngooŇč…óini mo adii mi mi yamirde= sakkitoore on? Pellet, …óuum …óoo ko fewjoore nde pewju…óon ka saare fii no njaltiniron toon yim…ďe mayre. ma on nganndu."
  7,124,"Ma mi ta∆īa juu…óe mon …óen e koy…óe mon …óeen (mi) luutindira, refti ma mi feta on denndaangal""."
  7,125,"∆Āe mbi'i : ""minen, ko faade ka Joomi amen woni ruttorde amen."
  7,126,"A a√Īiraani min si wanaa fii min ngooŇč…óinii maandeeji Joomi amen, tuma nde …ói ngarunoo amen. Joomi amen! Yuppu mu√Īal e amen, ∆īettitaa min ko min jebbilii …ďe.(juul…ďe)"
  7,127,"Mbatu yim…ďe Fir'awna ngun mbi'i : ""A accat Muusaa e yim…ďe mum …ďeen no bonnira ka leydi, o acce an e dewetee…ói maa …óin?!"" o wi'i : ""ma min mbar …ďi…ó…ďe ma…ď…ďe wor…ďe …ďeen men ngaccita …ďi…ó…ďe ma…ď…ďe rew…ďe …ďeen (nguura). Pellet, minen, e dow ma…ď…ďe ko min fooloo…ďe""."
  7,128,"Muusaa maakani yim…ďe makko …ďeen : ""mballinoree Alla mu√Ī√Īo…óon. Pellet, leydi ndin ka Alla woodani, Himo ronina ndi on mo o muuyi e jeyaa…ďe makko …ďeen. battane mo∆ī∆īe …óeen ko gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďeen woodani""."
  7,129,"∆Āe mbi'i : ""min lorranooma adii a arde amen e …ďaawo nde ngar…óaa e amen"". O maaki : ""Hino jortaa nde Joomi mon halkata ga√Īo mon O lomtina on ka leydi, O ndaara ko holno ngollirton""."
  7,130,"GooŇč…óii min nanngirii yim…ďe Fir'awna …ďe kokke e usytagol …ďesnooje ; mbelejo'o, …ďe mbaajitoto."
  7,131,"Si mo∆ī∆īere nden arii …ďe, …ďe mbi'a : ""mi…óen kaan di e ndee …óoo"" ; si bone on he…ďii …ďe, …ďe kiitinora Muusaa e won du…ďe e makko …ďeen. nganndee pellet, kiiti ma…ď…ďe …óin ko ka Alla iwri, kono ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e yim…ďe …ďen nganndaa."
  7,132,"∆Āe mbi'i : ""Kala ko ngaaddan …óaa min e kaawis fii no mbil…óoraa min …óuum ; min wonaani gooŇč…óinoo…ďe ma""."
  7,133,"Min ngurti e ma…ď…ďe waame, e kanu, e karan=tendi, e totiiji=paabi, e ∆īii∆īam, ko kaawisaaji pensitaa…ói, …ďe mawnintinii, …ďe laatii yim…ďe bon …ďe."
  7,134,"Tuma nde lepte …óeen njannoo e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe mbi'i : ""ko an Muusaa, torano amen Joomi maa sabu kon ko O ahodi e maa…óa. Si a huncanii amen …óee lepte, ma men ngooŇč…óine, ma min accide kadi e …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila …ďeen""."
  7,135,"Nde min kuŇčcannoo …ďe lepte …óeen haa e lajal ngal …ďe njottotoo, jaka yoo kam…ďe ko …ďe firtoo…ďe (ahadi ma…ď…ďe ndin)."
  7,136,"Min njottii e ma…ď…ďe ; minn njooliri …ďe ka maayo sabu ko …ďe njeddiri kon kaawisaaji amen …óiin, …ďe laatii welsindii…ďe e majje."
  7,137,"minn ndonnni yim…ďe wonnoo…ďe e lo'ineede …ďeen fu…ónaange leydi ndin e hiirnaange mayri ndi min mbarkini e mu'um. Konngol Joomi maa mo∆ī∆īongol ngol timmii e …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila …ďeen sabu ko …ďe mu√Ī√Īinoo kon. min kalki ko Fir'awna e yim…ďe mum …ďeen mo∆ī∆īinanynoo, e kon ko …ďe …ďamtaynoo (e ku…ďeeje)."
  7,138,"Min lummbini …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila …ďen maayo ngon, …ďe ndewi e yim…ďe √Īii…ďu…ďe (e dewugol) sanamuuji mu'un, …ďe mbi : ""ehey Muusaa, wa…óan amen dewetee…óo wano dewetee…ói woodirani …ďe non"". O maaki : ""Pellet, onon ko on yim…ďe majjoo…ďe""."
  7,139,"Pellet, …ďee …óoo, ko …ďe ngoni e mum kon ko kalkaa…óum, kadi ko mehre woni ko …ďe ngollatnoo."
  7,140,"E ko ko woori Alla mi …óa…ď…ďanta on dewetee…óo, KaŇčko O …ďurnii on e winndere ndeen?!""."
  7,141,"(ciftoree) tuma nde minn nda…óndunoo on e yim…ďe Fir'awna …ďeen, he…ďe mee…óna on lepte bon …óe : …ďe mbara …ďi…ó…ďe mon wor…ďe …ďe kedda rew…ďe mon …ďeen. No e …óuum moo…óon jarrabuyee maw…óo immorde ka Joomi mon."
  7,142,"Min haldidi e Muusaa jemmaaji cappan…ói tati, Min timminiri …ói sappo, happu Joomi makko on timmiri jemmaaji cappan…óe nayi. Muusaa maakani musi…ó…óo makko Haaruuna : ""Lomtom ka yim…ďe am, mo∆ī∆īinaa (fiyaake ma…ď…ďe), wata a jokku laawol bonnoo…ďe …ďeen""."
  7,143,"Nde Muusaa arunoo fii happu amen on Joomi makko yeewti mo, o maaki : ""Joomi, hollam mi ndaare!"" O Daali : ""A yi'ataa kam ; kono ndaar fello ngon : si ngo √Īii…ďii e nokku maggo, aray ka yi'at kam"". Nde Joomi makko fee√Īannoo fello ngon, O wa…óti ngo …óiggu ngo, Muusaa yani fa…ó…óaa. Nde o …óigtunoo, o maaki : ""Senaare woodani Ma! mi tuubanii ma, min ko mi arano e gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďeen""."
  7,144,"O Daali : ""Eehey ma Muusaa, min mi su…ďii ma e yim…ďe …ďeen Nule mm …óeen e konngol am ngol. Jogito ko mi jonnu maa kon njeyee…óaa e yettoo…ďe …ďeen""."
  7,145,"Min mbnndani mo ka alluuje kala huunde, waaju e fensitannde kala huunde. Jogitor nde doole, njamiraa yim…ďe maa …ďe jogitagol ko …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e mayre. Arma mi holla on galle yaltu…ďe …óoftaare …ďe"
  7,146,"Mi firto ga e Aayeeje Am …óe …ďeen mawnintinoray…ďe ka leydi ko aldaa e goonga. hay si …ďe nji'i kala kaawis …ďe ngooŇč…óintaa mo, si …ďe nji'ii laawol peewal ngol …ďe njogitotaako ngol laawol, si …ďe nji'ii laawol bewre ngol …ďe njogitoo ngol laawol. ∆äuum noon, ko tawde …ďe njeddii kaawniinde amen …óe, …ďe ngoni welsindii…ďe e majje."
  7,147,"∆Āeen yeddu…ďe kaawnii…óe amen …óen e kawraangal e laakara, golle ma…ď…ďe …óe mbonii. Hara …ďeen njo…ďoyte si wanaa kon ko …ďe ngollaynoo?"
  7,148,"Yim…ďe Muusa …ďeen njogitii …ďaawo makko cu…óaari ma…ď…ďe ndin ngaari …ďanndinnke, hindi mari nuunaango=kuunaali. E …ďe nji'aani won de ndi yewtidataa e ma…ď…ďe ndi fewntanaa …ďe kadi e laawol? ∆Āe njogitike ndii [ngaari reweteendi], …ďe laatii too√Īoo…ďe."
  7,149,"Nde yantunoo e juu…óe ma…ď…ďe, …ďe nji'i won de gooŇč…óii …ďe majjii, …ďe mb'i : ""Si Joomi amen yurmaaka amen, o yaafi men, pellet, min laatoday e hayru…ďe …ďen"".(pertu…ďe)"
  7,150,"Nde Muusaa ruttinoo e yim…ďe makko …ďen ko o tikku…óo, cunii…óo, o maaki : ""Bonii kon ko lomti…óon kam …ďaawo am. E on ke√Īor yamiroore Joomi mon nde?!"" O weddii alluuje …óeen o nanngi hoore (musi…ó…óo) neene-gooto makko on himo foo…óa mo e makko. [Haaruuna] Maaki : ""Ko an yo …ďi…ó…óo neene am, …ďee yim…ďe lo'inii kam, …ďe …óe…ďi'i warde kam. Wota a weltin a√Ī…ďe am, wata a wa…ótidam kadi e yim…ďe toono…ďe …ďe""."
  7,151,"O maaki : ""Joomi am, yaafom min e (musi…ó…óo)neene-gooto am on, naataa min ka yurmeende aa. Ko an woni …ďur…óo yurmeede e yurmetee…ďe …ďen""."
  7,152,"Pellet, …ďeen jogitii …ďe ngaari ndi (reweteendi), arma tikkere he…ďa …ďe immorde e Joomi ma…ď…ďe, e koyeera ka nguurndam aduna. Ko wano non min njo…ďirta fekintoo…ďe …ďeen."
  7,153,"∆Āeen gollu…ďe boneeji, refti …ďe tuubi …ďaawo …óuum …ďe ngooŇč…óini, pellet, Joomi maa, …ďaawo …óum, ko jafotoo…óo, jurmotoo…óo."
  7,154,"Nde tikkere nden dee∆īunoo e Muusaa, o ∆īetti alluuje …óen. Tawi no e binndoodi majje, peewal e yurmeende wonan de …ďeen huloo…ďe Joomi muen."
  7,155,"Muusaa su…ďii e yim…ďe makko …ďen wor…ďe cappan…óe njee…ói…óo fii happu amen. Nde dillaango ngon nanngunoo …ďe, o maaki : ""Joomi, si a muuyuno, A halkayno …ďe adii hannde, e min kadi. E A halkiray men ko …óaay…ďe amen …ďen ngollii? ∆äum wonaani si wanaa jarrabuyee maa…óa, Ha…óa majjinira …óum on mo muuyu-…óaa, Ha…óa feewna on mo muuyu-…óaa. Ko aan woni keeto amen, hafran amen njurme-…óaa amen. Ko aan woni …ďur…óo mo∆ī∆īude e yaafoo…ďe …ďe""."
  7,156,"Winndan amen ka aduna …óoo mo∆ī∆īere, e ka laakara. minen min tuubanii ma. O Daali : ""Lepte am …óe, mi meminay …óe on mo mi muuyi. Yurmeende am nden yaajanii kala huunde. arma mi winndana nde …ďen huloo…ďe (Alla), …ďe totta zakka, e …ďen ngooŇč…óinoo…ďe Aayeeje amen …óe""."
  7,157,"∆Āeen jokkat…ďe nulaa…óo on, annabaajo humammbinneejo, on mo …ďe tawta fii mum no winndaa ka ma…ď…ďe ka Tawreeta e ka Linnjiila. Homo yamira …ďe mo∆ī∆īere, o ha…óa …ďe Ňči√Īere, homo daginana …ďe dagii…ói …ói, o harminana …ďe co…ď…ói …óin, o ittana …ďe teddeelo e kolommbooje=tonngi wonunoo…óe e hoore-ma…ď…ďe. ∆Āen gooŇč…óin…ďe mo, …ďe teddini mo, …ďe walli mo, …ďe njokki annoore Jippinaa…óo won dude e makko ; …ďen, ko kam…ďe woni malaa…ďe …ďeen."
  7,158,"Maaku : ""Eey mon yim…ďe, min ko mi Nulaa…óo Alla e moo…óon on denndaangal, on mo woodani …óum laamu kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin. dewetee…óo alaa si wanaa kaŇčko. Homo wuurna wara. ngooŇč…óinee Alla e nulaa…óo makko annabaajo humammbinneejo on, on ngooŇč…óin…óo Alla e Konngu…ói makko …óin. njokkee mo, mbelejo'o, on peeway""."
  7,159,"Hino e yim…ďe Muusaa …ďeen, mofte (le√Īol)fewniray…óe (yim…ďe …ďen) e goonga, ko …óuum ngoni ko …ďe nuun…óiraa."
  7,160,"Min ceerndi …ďe gori sappo e …ói…ói (lenol). min wahyini e Muusaa tuma nde yim…ďe makko …ďeen …óa…ď…ďirnoo mo yarnineede won de : ""fiyir tuggordu maa ndun haa∆īre nden"". …ďulli sappo e …ói…ói yallti e mayre. GooŇč…óii gorol kala andii yarirde mu'm. min …óowdinirani …ďe duule, min Jippini e ma…ď…ďe demmbe-njuuri, e teewu colli. ""√Ďaamee e laa…ďu…ói …ói min arsiki on"". ∆Āe too√Īaani min, kono ko woŇčkiiji ma…ď…ďe …ďe too√Īatnoo."
  7,161,"Tuma nde …ďe mbi'anaa : ""ko…óee e ndee saare, √Īaamon e mayre nokku kala ka nji…óu…óon, mbion : …ďoran amen [goopi amen], naatiron ka damal ko on sujju…ďe, minn njaafoto on goopi mon. Arma min …ďeydana mo∆ī∆īim…ďe …ďeen""."
  7,162,"Too√Īu…ďe …ďen e ma…ď…ďe mbayliri konngol ngol ko wanaa ngol ngol …ďe mbiananoo. min njippini e ma…ď…ďe lepte immorde ka kammu, sabu ko …ďe laatinoo he…ďe too√Īa."
  7,163,"Naamno …ďe fii saare wonunoonde nden ka sera maayo, tuma nde …ďe jaggitaynoo e Aseweere nden, tuma nde li∆ī∆īi ma…ď…ďe …óin ngraynoo…ďe √Īalnde Aseweere ma…ď…ďe nden ko …ói kuywu…ói, √Īalnde woni wanaa aseweere ma…ď…ďe …ói ngrataa …ďe. Ko wano nii min jarriborta …ďe kon ko …ďe njaltatnooko …óoftaare"
  7,164,"Tuma nde dentaal jeyaa…óo e ma…ď…ďe wi'noo : ""Ko hol…óum mbaajoanto…óon yim…ďe, Allaahu ko kalkoowo …ďe maa O lepta …ďe lepte sattu…óe?"" …ďe mbi'i : ""Ko [ittugol] ngantu faade ka Joomi mo'on ; e belejo'o, kam…ďe …ďe ndentoto""."
  7,165,"Nde …ďe njejjitunoo ko …ďe mbaajanoo fii mum kon, minn nda…óndi …ďeen ha…óaynoo…ďe e bone on, minn nanngiri …ďeen too√Īu…ďe lepte sattu…óe sabu ko …ďe njalatnooko.e …óoftaare."
  7,166,"Nde …ďe townitaninoo e ko …ďe ka…óaa e mum kon, min mbi'ani …ďe : ""Laatee baa…ói jaasu…ói""."
  7,167,"siftor tuma nde Joomi maa anndinnoo (won de) ma o nulu e ma…ď…ďe haa √Ďalnde Darngal on mee…óinoowo …ďe lepte bon …óe. Pellet, Joomi maa ko jaawu…óe lepte, pellet kadi, ko O jaafotoo…óoo, jurmotoo…óo."
  7,168,"Men senndiri …ďe ka leydi dente : hino e ma…ď…ďe mo∆ī∆īu…ďe, hino e ma…ď…ďe ko jaasi …óum. min njarribori …ďe mo∆ī∆īu…ói e bo…ó…ói, mbelejo'o, kam…ďe …ďe nduttoto."
  7,169,"Lomtii …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe lomtii …ďe (bon…ďe), …ďe roni deftere nden, hi…ďe ∆īetta wee…ďitan…óe oo aduna …ďe mbi'a : ""Aray min njaaffee"". Si wee…ďitannde sugu mum arii e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe ∆īetta …óum.hara ahadi deftere nden ∆īettidaaka e ma…ď…ďe, won de wata …ďe wowlu e Alla si wanaa goonga?! …ďe janngi ko woni e mayre. Ko galle laakara …óen …ďuri mo∆ī∆īannde …ďen rentii…ďe. E on kakkiltaa?!"
  7,170,"∆Āeen jogitotoo…ďe deftere nden …ďe √Īii…ďna juulde, pellet, mien min yeebataa njo…ďdi mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe …ďeen."
  7,171,"Siftor tuma nde min …ďorunoo fello ngon senngo dow ma…ď…ďe, a sikkat ko ngo …óowdi.…ďe pelliti ngo yanat e ma…ď…ďe. ""njogitoree ko min ngokki on kon doole, jaŇčtee ko woni e mayre, mbelejo'o, on kulon Alla""."
  7,172,"siftoro kadi nde Joomi maa ∆īettunoo e …ďi…ó…ďe Aadama …ďen ka keeci ma…ď…ďe jurriiyaaji ma…ď…ďe …óin, O seendintini …ďe e woŇčkiiji ma…ď…ďe …óin : ""Wanaa kon min woni Joomi mon?"" …ďe mb'i : ""Ko non woniri, min seedike"". Ko fii (wata) on mb'oy √Ďande Darngal : ""minn min ngoniino welsindii…ďe e …óuum …óoo""."
  7,173,"Maa mbi'oyon : ""woni ko baabiraa…ďe amen …ďe cirkunoo ko adii, min wonti (tun) jurriiya …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe. E A halkiray men ko bonnoo…ďe …ďen mba…ói?"
  7,174,"Ko wano nii min fensitirta Aayeeje …óeen, e mbeleo'o kam…ďe …ďe nduttoto."
  7,175,"Janngan …ďe kumpite on mo min ngokkuno Aayeeje amen …óen, o …ďoorii …óe, seytaane jokki mo, e laatodii e majju…ďe …ďen(.bew…ďe…ďe)"
  7,176,"Sinno min muuyuno, min …ďamtirayno mo …óe, ko woni tun o heddike ka leydi o jokki belaa…óe makko. yeru makko ko sifa rawaandu, si a ronndii ndu ndu lahay, maa si a terti ndu du lahay. Ko …óuum woni misal yim…ďe yeddu…ďe Aayeeje amen …óeen. Fillo qissaaji …óin ; mbelejo'o, …ďe miijitoto."
  7,177,"[Alaa ko …ďuri] bon de misal …ďeen yim…ďe yeddu…ďe Aayeeje amen …óen, ko woŇčkiiji ma…ď…ďe woni ko …ďe too√Īaynoo."
  7,178,"Kala mo Alla feewni, ko on feewata ; kala kadi mo O majjini, ko …ďeen hayru…ďe …ďeen."
  7,179,"GooŇč…óii min taganii Jahannama ko …óuu…ói e jinna e yim…ďe. He…ďe mari …ďer…óe, …ďe faamirtaa …óe. Hi…ďe mari gite, …ďe njiirtaa …óe. Hi…ďe mari noppi, …ďe nanirtaa …ói. …ďeen no mb'i wa neemoraa…ói, toode ko kam…ďe …ďuri majjude. Ko …ďeen ngoni welsindii…ďe …ďen."
  7,180,"Ko Alla woodani in…óe …ďur…óe mo∆ī∆īude …óen. Noddiree Mo …óe, terto…óon …ďen oo√Īotoo…ďe ka in…óe makko : arma …ďe njo…ďoyee ko …ďe ngollaynoo."
  7,181,"Hino e …ďen …ďe Men tagi, mofte (le∆ī∆īi)feewiray…óe goonga, ko …óum kadi …ďe nuun…óirta."
  7,182,"∆Āeen yeddu…ďe Aayeeje amen …óen, min suyniray …ďe e nokku ka …ďe anganndaa."
  7,183,"Mi…óo nee…ďnana …ďe, pellet, pewje Am …óen ko tii…óu…óe."
  7,184,"E …ďee miijitaaki? gonndiijo ma…ď…ďe on aldaa e jinna : on wonaani si wanaa jeertinoowo …ďanngu…óo.(pee√Ī…óo)"
  7,185,"E …ďe ndaaraani laamuuji kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, e ko Alla tagi e piiji, e haawnaaki hara lajal ma…ď…ďe ngal …ďadike? E ko yewtere honnde …ďaawo ndee …óoo …ďe ngooŇč…óinta?!"
  7,186,"Kala mo Alla majjini, peewnoowo mo alaa. Himo acca …ďe e bewre ma…ď…ďe hi…ďe bumam-bumannoo .(mbumo)"
  7,187,"Hi…ďe naamno maa fii darngal : ""ko honnde woni daragol maggal?"" Maaku : "" ganndal mum ko ka Joomi am woni. Alaa fe√Ī√Īioowo waqtu maggal on si wanaa KaŇčko. Ngal teddii ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Ngal arataa e mon si wanaa e juhal"". Hi…ďe la…ďndo maa a sikkay ko a ku…ďindii…óo e …óum. Maaku : ""ganndal mum ko ka Alla woni"". kono ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e yim…ďe …ďen ngnndaa […óum]."
  7,188,"Maaku : ""Mi waawanaa hoore-am nafa wanaa lorra, si wanaa ko Alla muuyi. Sinno mi…óo anndunoo ko wirnii, mi hebbinorayno mo∆ī∆īere, bone kadi memataano kam. mi wonaani si wanaa jeertinoowo e bewlinoowo, wonan de yim…ďe gooŇč…óinoo…ďe""."
  7,189,"Ko KaŇčko woni tak…óo on immorde e woŇčkii gooti, o wa…ói e makki genndo makko, fii yo o dee∆īu e makko. tuma nde o renndunoo e makko, o sowii sowannde hoyfunde, o duumodi e mun. Nde o teddidunoo [e reedu ndun], …ďe torodi Alla Joomi ma…ď…ďe : ""Pellet, si a wee…óii amen (…ďi…ó…óo) yottii…óo, ma min njeye e yettoo…ďe Ma …ďeen""."
  7,190,"Nde O wee…ónoo …ďe (…ďi…ó…óo) yottii…óo, …ďe wa…óidani Mo kafidii…ďe e kon ko o ye…ói …ďe. Alla toowii e kon ko …ďe corkata."
  7,191,"E …ďe kafiday (mo) e kon ko tagataa hay e huunde, kam…ďe tigi ko …ďe tagaa…ďe?!"
  7,192,"∆äi waawanaa …ďe ballal, wanaa (hay) ko'e majji …ói mballata."
  7,193,"Si on noddii …ói e peewal, …ói njokkataa on. Hino fotanion , si on noddii …ói maa hara ko on dey∆īu…ďe."
  7,194,"Pellet, …óiin …ói noddoton gah Alla, ko jeyaa…ói yeruuji mon. Noddee …ói, yo …ói njaabinanii on, si on laatike gooŇč…óu…ďe."
  7,195,"Hara hi…ói mari koy…óe ko …ói yahra? kaa hi…ói mari juu…óe ko …ói du√Īira? Kaa hi…ói mari gite ko …ói nji'ira? Kaa hi…ói mari noppi ko …ói nanira? maaku : ""Noddee kafidii…ói mon …óiin, refti pewjanon kam, wata on nee…ďtiitanam""."
  7,196,"Pellet, ko Alla woni keetam on, On Jippin…óo deftetere nden, ko KaŇčko woni keet mo∆ī∆īu…ďe …ďen."
  7,197,"∆äin …ói noddoton gah mo, …ói kattanaa e wallude on, wanaa kadi ko'e majji …ói mballata."
  7,198,"Si on noddii …ói e peewal, …ói nanataa. ha…óa yi'a hi…ói hi…óima ndaara, (kono) kaŇčji …ói yi'ataa."
  7,199,"Jogito yaafuyee, njamiraa mo∆ī∆īere nden …óuurno-…óaa e majju…ďe …ďeen."
  7,200,"Si sowinsinoore arii he…ďude ma immorde e seytaane, moolor Alla. KaŇčko ko O nanoowo, ganndu…óo."
  7,201,"Pellet, …ďeen hul…ď…ďe(Alla), si sowonsinoore he…ďii …ďe immorde e sytaane, …ďe ngannditay [Alla] : jaka yoo kam…ďe ko …ďe yi'oo…ďe."
  7,202,"Musi…ď…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen [ka yim…ďe] hino foo…óa …ďe e bewre, refti …ďe ra…ď…ďintaako."
  7,203,"Si a addanaani …ďe Aaya, …ďe mbi'a : ""Ko ha…ónoo sincaa …óum?""(pekindo…óa) Maaku : ""Anndee ko jokku-mi, ko kon wahyina e am immorde ka Joomi am. Ndee …óoo [Alqur'aanaare] ko hujjaaji (…ďanngu…ói) immorde ka Joomi mon, e peewal e yurmeende wonnande yim…ďe gom…óinoo…ďe""."
  7,204,"Si Alqur'aana no janngeede, ke…ótee nde de∆ī∆īiton ; mbelejo'o, on njurminte."
  7,205,"Siftor Joomi maa…óa ka woŇčkii maa, ka yankinaare e ka kulol, ko aldaa e fe√Ī√Īingol konngol, bimmbi e kiikii…óe, wata a laatodo e welsindii…ďe …ďen."
  7,206,"Pellet, …ďeen [maleykaaji] won …ďe ka Joomi maa, …ďe townitantaako dewgol Mo, hi…ďe subbunhinanoo Mo, ko KaŇčko woni ko …ďe cujjanta."
